      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/metlife-is-said-to-near-deal-to-buy-hk-tycoon-li-s-pinebridge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国保险公司大都会人寿保险公司 (MetLife Inc.) 即将达成协议，从香港亿万富翁李泽楷的盈科拓展集团手中收购 PineBridge Investments 在中国以外的资产。]]></description>
